### Extended Unique Identifier 64

| STEP                                         | MAC                    |
| ---                                          | ---                    |
| 1. Identify the MAC Address of the interface | aabb.cc00.0230         |
| 2. Insert FFFE in the Middle                 | aabb.cc  fffe  00.0230 |
| 3. Flip the 7th bit from the left            | :a8bb:ccff:fe00:0230:  |

<br>

__aabb.cc00.0930__
~~~
!@R4
conf t
 int e0/3
  no shut
  ipv6 add fd00:4::/64 eui-64
  end
~~~

__aabb.cc00.0a30__
~~~
!@R3
conf t
 int e0/3
  no shut
  ipv6 add fd00:4::/64 eui-64
  end
~~~


<br>

